  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "Nizzuf's Maze was a grand hedge maze created by the arch-mage Nizzuf for his amusement. The maze boasted hundreds of magical traps, most of them extremely lethal. Nizzuf posted a reward big enough to buy a kingdom to the man or woman brave enough to enter the maze and reach its core. Thousands tried and died.  But one, Oteg Verm completed the maze, thanks mainly to this ring which let him 'see' where the traps were hidden."
    }
